form duration-500 group-hover:scale-110\" > </div> <div class\u003d\"p-5\"> <h3 class\u003d\"text-xl font-bold text-dark mb-2\">迷你香蕉</h3> <p class\u003d\"text-gray-600 mb-4\"> 体型小巧，长度约10厘米，口感特别甜，适合儿童和便携零食。 </p> <el-tag type\u003d\"success\" class\u003d\"mr-2 mb-2\">零食</el-tag> <el-tag type\u003d\"info\" class\u003d\"mr-2 mb-2\">儿童食品</el-tag> </div> </el-card> </el-col> <el-col :xs\u003d\"24\" :sm\u003d\"12\" :md\u003d\"8\" class\u003d\"mb-8\"> <el-card class\u003d\"h-full overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl group\"> <div class\u003d\"relative overflow-hidden h-48\"> <img src\u003d\"https://picsum.photos/id/105/500/300\" alt\u003d\"苹果香蕉\" class\u003d\"w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-110\" > </div> <div class\u003d\"p-5\"> <h3 class\u003d\"text-xl font-bold text-dark mb-2\">苹果香蕉</h3> <p class\u003d\"text-gray-600 mb-4\"> 带有苹果的淡淡香气，口感清脆，甜度适中，适合直接食用。 </p> <el-tag type\u003d\"success\" class\u003d\"mr-2 mb-2\">直接食用</el-tag> <el-tag type\u003d\"info\" class\u003d\"mr-2 mb-2\">水果沙拉</el-tag> </div> </el-card> </el-col> <el-col :xs\u003d\"24\" :sm\u003d\"12\" :md\u003d\"8\" class\u003d\"mb-8\"> <el-card class\u003d\"h-full overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl group\"> <div class\u003d\"relative overflow-hidden h-48\"> <img src\u003d\"https://picsum.photos/id/104/500/300\" alt\u003d\"蓝香蕉\" class\u003d\"w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-110\" > </div> <div class\u003d\"p-5\"> <h3 class\u003d\"text-xl font-bold text-dark mb-2\">蓝香蕉</h3> <p class\u003d\"text-gray-600 mb-4\"> 表皮呈蓝绿色，果肉呈淡黄色，口感细腻，带有淡淡香草味。 </p> <el-tag type\u003d\"success\" class\u003d\"mr-2 mb-2\">甜点</el-tag> <el-tag type\u003d\"info\" class\u003d\"mr-2 mb-2\">冰淇淋</el-tag> </div> </el-card> </el-col> </el-row> </div> </div> </section> <!-- 营养价值部分 --> <section id\u003d\"nutrition\" class\u003d\"py-16 md:py-24 bg-white\"> <div class\u003d\"container mx-auto px-4\"> <div class\u003d\"text-center mb-16\"> <h2 class\u003d\"text-[clamp(1.8rem,4vw,2.5rem)] font-bold text-dark mb-4\">营养价值</h2> <p class\u003d\"text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto\"> 香蕉不仅美味，还是一种营养密集型水果，富含多种维生素、矿物质和抗氧化物质。 </p> <div class\u003d\"w-20 h-1 bg-primary mx-auto rounded-full mt-4\"></div> </div> <div class\u003d\"flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-12\"> <div class\u003d\"lg:w-1/2\"> <div class\u003d\"bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8 shadow-sm\"> <h3 class\u003d\"text-xl font-bold text-dark mb-6\">一个中等大小香蕉的营养成分</h3> <el-table :data\u003d\"nutritionData\" border class\u003d\"mb-6\"> <el-table-column prop\u003d\"nutrient\" label\u003d\"营养素\" width\u003d\"160\"></el-table-column> <el-table-column prop\u003d\"amount\" label\u003d\"含量\"></el-table-column> <el-table-column prop\u003d\"daily\" label\u003d\"每日需求量占比\"></el-table-column> </el-table> <div class\u003d\"bg-primary/10 p-4 rounded-lg\"> <h4 class\u003d\"font-bold text-dark mb-2 flex items-center\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-lightbulb-o text-primary mr-2\"></i> 营养小贴士 </h4> <p class\u003d\"text-gray-600 text-sm\"> 香蕉是钾的极佳来源，有助于维持正常的心跳和血压。同时，香蕉中的天然糖分（葡萄糖、果糖和蔗糖）能快速补充能量，是运动前后的理想零食。 </p> </div> </div> </div> <div class\u003d\"lg:w-1/2\"> <div class\u003d\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\"> <div class\u003d\"bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/10 to-primary/20 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow\"> <div class\u003d\"text-primary text-3xl mb-4\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-heartbeat\"></i> </div> <h3 class\u003d\"text-xl font-bold text-dark mb-2\">心脏健康</h3> <p class\u003d\"text-gray-600\"> 高钾含量有助于降低血压，减少心血管疾病风险，维持心脏正常功能。 </p> </div> <div class\u003d\"bg-gradient-to-br from-secondary/10 to-secondary/20 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow\"> <div class\u003d\"text-secondary text-3xl mb-4\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-brain\"></i> </div> <h3 class\u003d\"text-xl font-bold text-dark mb-2\">大脑功能</h3> <p class\u003d\"text-gray-600\"> 含有维生素B6，有助于产生血清素和多巴胺，改善情绪和减轻压力。 </p> </div> <div class\u003d\"bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/10 to-accent/20 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow\"> <div class\u003d\"text-accent text-3xl mb-4\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-bolt\"></i> </div> <h3 class\u003d\"text-xl font-bold text-dark mb-2\">能量补充</h3> <p class\u003d\"text-gray-600\"> 天然糖分和碳水化合物组合，提供快速且持续的能量释放。 </p> </div> <div class\u003d\"bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-100 to-blue-200 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow\"> <div class\u003d\"text-blue-500 text-3xl mb-4\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-dumbbell\"></i> </div> <h3 class\u003d\"text-xl font-bold text-dark mb-2\">肌肉功能</h3> <p class\u003d\"text-gray-600\"> 钾有助于预防肌肉痉挛，是运动员和健身爱好者的理想选择。 </p> </div> <div class\u003d\"bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-100 to-purple-200 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow\"> <div class\u003d\"text-purple-500 text-3xl mb-4\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-digestive\"></i> </div> <h3 class\u003d\"text-xl font-bold text-dark mb-2\">消化系统</h3> <p class\u003d\"text-gray-600\"> 富含膳食纤维，促进肠道蠕动，有助于维持消化系统健康。 </p> </div> <div class\u003d\"bg-gradient-to-br from-green-100 to-green-200 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow\"> <div class\u003d\"text-green-500 text-3xl mb-4\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-shield\"></i> </div> <h3 class\u003d\"text-xl font-bold text-dark mb-2\">免疫系统</h3> <p class\u003d\"text-gray-600\"> 维生素C和抗氧化物质增强免疫力，帮助身体抵抗感染和疾病。 </p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <!-- 营养对比图表 --> <div class\u003d\"mt-16\"> <h3 class\u003d\"text-xl font-bold text-dark mb-6 text-center\">香蕉与其他水果的营养对比</h3> <div class\u003d\"bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-xl shadow-sm\"> <el-row> <el-col :xs\u003d\"24\" :md\u003d\"12\" class\u003d\"mb-6 md:mb-0\"> <el-card class\u003d\"border-0 shadow-none bg-transparent\"> <template #header> <div class\u003d\"text-left font-bold text-dark\">主要矿物质含量对比 (mg/100g)</div> </template> <el-chart height\u003d\"300\"> <el-bar :data\u003d\"mineralData\" :x-field\u003d\"'name'\" :y-field\u003d\"'value'\" :series-field\u003d\"'type'\"> <el-tooltip formatter\u003d\"{}: {}mg\"></el-tooltip> </el-bar> </el-chart> </el-card> </el-col> <el-col :xs\u003d\"24\" :md\u003d\"12\"> <el-card class\u003d\"border-0 shadow-none bg-transparent\"> <template #header> <div class\u003d\"text-left font-bold text-dark\">维生素含量对比 (mg/100g)</div> </template> <el-chart height\u003d\"300\"> <el-line :data\u003d\"vitaminData\" :x-field\u003d\"'name'\" :y-field\u003d\"'value'\" :series-field\u003d\"'type'\"> <el-tooltip formatter\u003d\"{}: {}mg\"></el-tooltip> </el-line> </el-chart> </el-card> </el-col> </el-row> </div> </div> </div> </section> <!-- 香蕉食谱部分 --> <section id\u003d\"recipes\" class\u003d\"py-16 md:py-24 bg-gray-50\"> <div class\u003d\"container mx-auto px-4\"> <div class\u003d\"text-center mb-16\"> <h2 class\u003d\"text-[clamp(1.8rem,4vw,2.5rem)] font-bold text-dark mb-4\">香蕉食谱</h2> <p class\u003d\"text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto\"> 香蕉是一种多用途的水果，可以用于制作各种美味的甜点和健康食品。探索以下简单又美味的香蕉食谱。 </p> <div class\u003d\"w-20 h-1 bg-primary mx-auto rounded-full mt-4\"></div> </div> <el-tabs v-model\u003d\"activeRecipeTab\" class\u003d\"w-full\"> <el-tab-pane label\u003d\"早餐\" name\u003d\"breakfast\"> <el-row :gutter\u003d\"20\" class\u003d\"mt-8\"> <el-col :xs\u003d\"24\" :md\u003d\"12\" class\u003d\"mb-8\"> <el-card class\u003d\"overflow-hidden h-full group\"> <div class\u003d\"flex flex-col md:flex-row h-full\"> <div class\u003d\"md:w-2/5 relative overflow-hidden\"> <img src\u003d\"https://picsum.photos/id/292/400/300\" alt\u003d\"香蕉燕麦粥\" class\u003d\"w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-110\" > </div> <div class\u003d\"md:w-3/5 p-5 flex flex-col\"> <h3 class\u003d\"text-xl font-bold text-dark mb-2\">香蕉燕麦粥</h3> <p class\u003d\"text-gray-600 mb-4 flex-grow\"> 健康营养的早餐选择，将燕麦与香蕉、牛奶一起煮制，撒上坚果和蜂蜜，美味又饱腹。 </p> <div class\u003d\"flex justify-between items-center\"> <div class\u003d\"flex items-center text-sm text-gray-500\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-clock-o mr-1\"></i> 10分钟 <span class\u003d\"mx-2\">|</span> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-signal mr-1\"></i> 简单 </div> <el-button type\u003d\"text\" class\u003d\"text-primary hover:text-primary/80 p-0\" @click\u003d\"showRecipeDetails('oatmeal')\" > 查看食谱 <i class\u003d\"fa fa-arrow-right ml-1\"></i> </el-button> </div> </div> </div> </el-card> </el-col> <el-col :xs\u003d\"24\" :md\u003d\"12\" class\u003d\"mb-8\"> <el-card class\u003d\"overflow-hidden h-full group\"> <div class\u003d\"flex flex-col md:flex-row h-full\"> <div class\u003d\"md:w-2/5 relative overflow-hidden\"> <img src\u003d\"https://picsum.photos/id/225/400/300\" alt\u003d\"香蕉松饼\" class\u003d\"w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-110\" > </div> <div class\u003d\"md:w-3/5 p-5 flex flex-col\"> <h3 class\u003d\"text-xl font-bold text-dark mb-2\">香蕉松饼</h3> <p class\u003d\"text-gray-600 mb-4 flex-grow\"> 用熟透的香蕉制作的松饼，无需额外加糖，口感松软香甜，是早餐或下午茶的理想选择。 </p> <div class\u003d\"flex justify-between items-center\"> <div class\u003d\"flex items-center text-sm text-gray-500\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-clock-o mr-1\"></i> 25分钟 <span class\u003d\"mx-2\">|</span> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-signal mr-1\"></i> 中等 </div> <el-button type\u003d\"text\" class\u003d\"text-primary hover:text-primary/80 p-0\" @click\u003d\"showRecipeDetails('muffin')\" > 查看食谱 <i class\u003d\"fa fa-arrow-right ml-1\"></i> </el-button> </div> </div> </div> </el-card> </el-col> </el-row> </el-tab-pane> <el-tab-pane label\u003d\"甜点\" name\u003d\"dessert\"> <el-row :gutter\u003d\"20\" class\u003d\"mt-8\"> <el-col :xs\u003d\"24\" :md\u003d\"12\" class\u003d\"mb-8\"> <el-card class\u003d\"overflow-hidden h-full group\"> <div class\u003d\"flex flex-col md:flex-row h-full\"> <div class\u003d\"md:w-2/5 relative overflow-hidden\"> <img src\u003d\"https://picsum.photos/id/291/400/300\" alt\u003d\"香蕉冰淇淋\" class\u003d\"w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-110\" > </div> <div class\u003d\"md:w-3/5 p-5 flex flex-col\"> <h3 class\u003d\"text-xl font-bold text-dark mb-2\">香蕉冰淇淋</h3> <p class\u003d\"text-gray-600 mb-4 flex-grow\"> 健康无添加的冰淇淋替代品，只需将冷冻香蕉放入搅拌机中搅打至顺滑即可享用。 </p> <div class\u003d\"flex justify-between items-center\"> <div class\u003d\"flex items-center text-sm text-gray-500\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-clock-o mr-1\"></i> 5分钟 <span class\u003d\"mx-2\">|</span> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-signal mr-1\"></i> 简单 </div> <el-button type\u003d\"text\" class\u003d\"text-primary hover:text-primary/80 p-0\" @click\u003d\"showRecipeDetails('icecream')\" > 查看食谱 <i class\u003d\"fa fa-arrow-right ml-1\"></i> </el-button> </div> </div> </div> </el-card> </el-col> <el-col :xs\u003d\"24\" :md\u003d\"12\" class\u003d\"mb-8\"> <el-card class\u003d\"overflow-hidden h-full group\"> <div class\u003d\"flex flex-col md:flex-row h-full\"> <div class\u003d\"md:w-2/5 relative overflow-hidden\"> <img src\u003d\"https://picsum.photos/id/132/400/300\" alt\u003d\"香蕉巧克力蛋糕\" class\u003d\"w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-110\" > </div> <div class\u003d\"md:w-3/5 p-5 flex flex-col\"> <h3 class\u003d\"text-xl font-bold text-dark mb-2\">香蕉巧克力蛋糕</h3> <p class\u003d\"text-gray-600 mb-4 flex-grow\"> 湿润松软的香蕉蛋糕，加入巧克力碎片，口感丰富，是派对和聚会的理想甜点。 </p> <div class\u003d\"flex justify-between items-center\"> <div class\u003d\"flex items-center text-sm text-gray-500\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-clock-o mr-1\"></i> 45分钟 <span class\u003d\"mx-2\">|</span> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-signal mr-1\"></i> 中等 </div> <el-button type\u003d\"text\" class\u003d\"text-primary hover:text-primary/80 p-0\" @click\u003d\"showRecipeDetails('cake')\" > 查看食谱 <i class\u003d\"fa fa-arrow-right ml-1\"></i> </el-button> </div> </div> </div> </el-card> </el-col> </el-row> </el-tab-pane> <el-tab-pane label\u003d\"饮品\" name\u003d\"drinks\"> <el-row :gutter\u003d\"20\" class\u003d\"mt-8\"> <el-col :xs\u003d\"24\" :md\u003d\"12\" class\u003d\"mb-8\"> <el-card class\u003d\"overflow-hidden h-full group\"> <div class\u003d\"flex flex-col md:flex-row h-full\"> <div class\u003d\"md:w-2/5 relative overflow-hidden\"> <img src\u003d\"https://picsum.photos/id/225/400/300\" alt\u003d\"香蕉奶昔\" class\u003d\"w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-110\" > </div> <div class\u003d\"md:w-3/5 p-5 flex flex-col\"> <h3 class\u003d\"text-xl font-bold text-dark mb-2\">香蕉奶昔</h3> <p class\u003d\"text-gray-600 mb-4 flex-grow\"> 将香蕉、牛奶和冰块放入搅拌机中搅打，制作出顺滑可口的奶昔，可加入蛋白粉增加营养。 </p> <div class\u003d\"flex justify-between items-center\"> <div class\u003d\"flex items-center text-sm text-gray-500\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-clock-o mr-1\"></i> 3分钟 <span class\u003d\"mx-2\">|</span> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-signal mr-1\"></i> 简单 </div> <el-button type\u003d\"text\" class\u003d\"text-primary hover:text-primary/80 p-0\" @click\u003d\"showRecipeDetails('smoothie')\" > 查看食谱 <i class\u003d\"fa fa-arrow-right ml-1\"></i> </el-button> </div> </div> </div> </el-card> </el-col> <el-col :xs\u003d\"24\" :md\u003d\"12\" class\u003d\"mb-8\"> <el-card class\u003d\"overflow-hidden h-full group\"> <div class\u003d\"flex flex-col md:flex-row h-full\"> <div class\u003d\"md:w-2/5 relative overflow-hidden\"> <img src\u003d\"https://picsum.photos/id/1080/400/300\" alt\u003d\"香蕉冰咖啡\" class\u003d\"w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-110\" > </div> <div class\u003d\"md:w-3/5 p-5 flex flex-col\"> <h3 class\u003d\"text-xl font-bold text-dark mb-2\">香蕉冰咖啡</h3> <p class\u003d\"text-gray-600 mb-4 flex-grow\"> 将香蕉、冷咖啡、牛奶和冰块混合，制作出提神醒脑的冰咖啡，是夏日的完美饮品。 </p> <div class\u003d\"flex justify-between items-center\"> <div class\u003d\"flex items-center text-sm text-gray-500\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-clock-o mr-1\"></i> 5分钟 <span class\u003d\"mx-2\">|</span> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-signal mr-1\"></i> 简单 </div> <el-button type\u003d\"text\" class\u003d\"text-primary hover:text-primary/80 p-0\" @click\u003d\"showRecipeDetails('coffee')\" > 查看食谱 <i class\u003d\"fa fa-arrow-right ml-1\"></i> </el-button> </div> </div> </div> </el-card> </el-col> </el-row> </el-tab-pane> </el-tabs> </div> </section> <!-- 常见问题部分 --> <section id\u003d\"faq\" class\u003d\"py-16 md:py-24 bg-white\"> <div class\u003d\"container mx-auto px-4\"> <div class\u003d\"text-center mb-16\"> <h2 class\u003d\"text-[clamp(1.8rem,4vw,2.5rem)] font-bold text-dark mb-4\">常见问题</h2> <p class\u003d\"text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto\"> 关于香蕉的常见问题解答，帮助您更好地了解和享用这种美味水果。 </p> <div class\u003d\"w-20 h-1 bg-primary mx-auto rounded-full mt-4\"></div> </div> <div class\u003d\"max-w-3xl mx-auto\"> <el-collapse accordion class\u003d\"border rounded-lg overflow-hidden\"> <el-collapse-item title\u003d\"如何挑选成熟的香蕉？\" name\u003d\"1\" class\u003d\"border-b last:border-b-0\"> <div class\u003d\"text-gray-600\"> 挑选香蕉时，可以根据果皮颜色判断成熟度：青绿色表示未成熟，甜度较低；亮黄色带有少量褐色斑点的香蕉成熟度适中，口感最佳；全黄色带有较多褐色斑点的香蕉甜度最高，适合制作烘焙食品。 </div> </el-collapse-item> <el-collapse-item title\u003d\"香蕉应该如何储存？\" name\u003d\"2\" class\u003d\"border-b last:border-b-0\"> <div class\u003d\"text-gray-600\"> 未成熟的香蕉可以室温存放，避免阳光直射。如果想加速成熟，可以将香蕉与苹果或西红柿放在一起。成熟的香蕉可以放入冰箱冷藏，虽然果皮会变黑，但果肉仍然新鲜，可延长保存时间3-5天。 </div> </el-collapse-item> <el-collapse-item title\u003d\"香蕉皮变黑了还能吃吗？\" name\u003d\"3\" class\u003d\"border-b last:border-b-0\"> <div class\u003d\"text-gray-600\"> 香蕉皮变黑通常是由于氧化作用，这并不意味着果肉变质。只要果肉没有变软流水或出现异味，仍然可以安全食用。实际上，表皮有褐色斑点的香蕉含有更高的抗氧化物质。 </div> </el-collapse-item> <el-collapse-item title\u003d\"香蕉对减肥有帮助吗？\" name\u003d\"4\" class\u003d\"border-b last:border-b-0\"> <div class\u003d\"text-gray-600\"> 香蕉含有天然糖分和膳食纤维，可以提供持久的饱腹感，有助于控制食欲。适量食用香蕉（每天1-2个）作为均衡饮食的一部分，可以辅助减肥。但过量食用可能导致热量摄入过多。 </div> </el-collapse-item> <el-collapse-item title\u003d\"香蕉可以空腹吃吗？\" name\u003d\"5\" class\u003d\"border-b last:border-b-0\"> <div class\u003d\"text-gray-600\"> 健康人群空腹适量食用香蕉是可以的。香蕉含有丰富的钾和镁，有些人担心空腹食用会影响心脏功能，但实际上正常食用量不会有问题。对于有胃病或胃酸过多的人，建议饭后食用。 </div> </el-collapse-item> <el-collapse-item title\u003d\"香蕉有哪些药用价值？\" name\u003d\"6\"> <div class\u003d\"text-gray-600\"> 香蕉在传统医学中有多种用途：缓解便秘（富含膳食纤维）、缓解胃酸过多（碱性水果）、补充运动后流失的电解质、缓解经前综合症症状等。香蕉皮也有一定的药用价值，可用于缓解蚊虫叮咬和皮肤瘙痒。 </div> </el-collapse-item> </el-collapse> </div> <div class\u003d\"mt-16 bg-primary/10 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-10 text-center\"> <h3 class\u003d\"text-2xl font-bold text-dark mb-4\">还有其他问题？</h3> <p class\u003d\"text-gray-600 mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto\"> 如果您有关于香蕉的其他问题，欢迎随时联系我们，我们的专家团队将为您提供详细解答。 </p> <el-button type\u003d\"primary\" size\u003d\"large\" class\u003d\"bg-primary hover:bg-primary/90 text-dark font-medium rounded-full px-8\" > 联系我们 </el-button> </div> </div> </section> <!-- 页脚 --> <footer class\u003d\"bg-dark text-white py-12\"> <div class\u003d\"container mx-auto px-4\"> <div class\u003d\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 mb-8\"> <div> <div class\u003d\"flex items-center space-x-2 mb-4\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-banana text-primary text-2xl\"></i> <h3 class\u003d\"text-xl font-bold\">香蕉百科</h3> </div> <p class\u003d\"text-gray-400 mb-4\"> 探索香蕉世界，了解这种神奇水果的一切。从品种到营养，从食谱到健康益处。 </p> <div class\u003d\"flex space-x-4\"> <a href\u003d\"#\" class\u003d\"text-gray-400 hover:text-primary transition-colors\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-facebook\"></i> </a> <a href\u003d\"#\" class\u003d\"text-gray-400 hover:text-primary transition-colors\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-twitter\"></i> </a> <a href\u003d\"#\" class\u003d\"text-gray-400 hover:text-primary transition-colors\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-instagram\"></i> </a> <a href\u003d\"#\" class\u003d\"text-gray-400 hover:text-primary transition-colors\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-youtube\"></i> </a> </div> </div> <div> <h4 class\u003d\"text-lg font-bold mb-4\">快速链接</h4> <ul class\u003d\"space-y-2\"> <li><a href\u003d\"#\" class\u003d\"text-gray-400 hover:text-primary transition-colors\">首页</a></li> <li><a href\u003d\"#intro\" class\u003d\"text-gray-400 hover:text-primary transition-colors\">香蕉简介</a></li> <li><a href\u003d\"#varieties\" class\u003d\"text-gray-400 hover:text-primary transition-colors\">香蕉品种</a></li> <li><a href\u003d\"#nutrition\" class\u003d\"text-gray-400 hover:text-primary transition-colors\">营养价值</a></li> <li><a href\u003d\"#recipe